Steps followed to solve the exersice
- docker run -it ubuntu (To run ubuntu and be able to interact with it)
- apt update && apt upgrade (To update packages)
- apt install curl  (Installing curl)
- curl --version (Verifying that cURL has been installed correctly)
- sh -c 'while true; do echo "Input website:"; read website; echo "Searching.."; sleep 1; curl http://$website; done'.   (Exercise command)